- Unit test: Exit conditions
- E2E test: Full watch cycle with completions","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-19T21:54:43.182014392Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-19T21:55:33.440466436Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
